Class PredictionExecutor

      • requestResourcesList

        public void requestResourcesList()
        Request that the MX framework list the available MX plugins and models and then issue callbacks to the application when either of those resources change. setMxListResourcesCallback(MXListResourcesCallback) must be called before requesting the resources list.

      • pluginLabelToID

        public static java.lang.String pluginLabelToID(java.lang.String pluginLabel)
        Extract a plugin ID from a plugin label.

        The list of plugins delivered by the MX framework are stylized as labels of the format "Plugin Name (Plugin ID)." This method extracts the plugin ID for an application, which can be used in requests to the MX framework.

        Parameters:
        pluginLabel - the plugin label from which to extract an ID.
        Returns:
        a plugin ID.

      • modelLabelToName

        public static java.lang.String modelLabelToName(java.lang.String modelLabel)
        Extract a model name from a model label.

        The list of models delivered by the MX framework are stylized as labels of the format "Model Name (Location)." This method extracts the model name for an application, which can be used in requests to the MX framework.

        Parameters:
        modelLabel - the model label from which to extract a model name.
        Returns:
        a model name.

      • requestRegisteredSensors

        public boolean requestRegisteredSensors()
        Request that the application be updated on available sensors.

        setSensorListQueryCallback(SensorListQueryCallback) should be called first to set the callback that receives the updates.

      • requestTAKMLFrameworkAppDataDirectory

        public void requestTAKMLFrameworkAppDataDirectory()
        Request the TAKML Framework's app data directory, so that app specific data can be loaded. setAppDataDirectoryQueryCallback(TAKMLAppDataDirectoryQueryCallback) must be called before requesting the TAKML Framework's app data directory.

      • requestTAKMLFrameworkAppDataDirectoryResourcesList
